# WKT of countries and cities

Well-known text representation of geometry (WKT) of countries and cities sourced from OpenStreetMap. Geometries were slightly simplified to improve database performance.

Below sections follow the naming convention of `Country/City (relation id)`.

## Extracting polygon

To extract polygon of country/city follow below steps:

1. Go to [openstreetmap](https://www.openstreetmap.org) website.
1. Search for place of your interest (country, city, etc.).
1. Select place of your interest from results.
1. Copy **relation id** (string of numbers in parentheses).
1. Go to [polygons.openstreetmap](https://polygons.openstreetmap.fr/) website.
1. Pass **relation id** into the input and submit form.
1. Click generate simplified polygon (optional).
1. Click `WKT` link, and copy `POLYGON(...)`.
